title: DIALOGUES WITH SOCIAL ROBOTS
description: Author: Kristiina Jokinen, Graham Wilcock Edition: 1st ed. 2017 edition Publication Date: May 9, 2017 Publisher: Springer ISBN-10: 9811025843 ISBN-13: 978-9811025846 Pages: 489 pages Format: pdf Size: 13M --- This book explores novel aspects of social robotics, spoken dialogue systems, human-robot interaction, spoken language understanding, multimodal communication, and system evaluation. It offers a variety of perspectives on and solutions to the most important questions about advanced techniques for social robots and chat systems. --- http://dlfeb.com/book/dialogues-with-social-robots-enablements-analyses-and-evaluation-lecture-notes-in-electrical-engineering/
